  "title": "Administrative Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>About AP Media</strong></p><p>AP Media is a creative media tech company that represents a new multi-disciplinary intersection point in the industry. At a time when audiences are craving for more immersive digital content, we are here to provide the technical expertise, experimental thinking and marketing innovation brands need to thrive.</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Familiar with local employment act and good HR practices.</li><li>Handle daily phone Calls and Incoming / outgoing emails</li><li>Conducts interview and assessment of applicants</li><li>Willing to learn and apply new grants</li><li>Purchasing of office supplies and stationery</li><li>Liaising with suppliers to ensure working office facilities</li><li>Assist in organising events for staff</li><li>Documentation filing </li><li>Maintain cleanliness of pantry</li><li>Manage inventory of IT equipment and basic IT troubleshooting</li><li>Demonstrated ability to accept responsibility & work effectively both independently& with a team</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>‘Can do’ work attitude is a must.</li><li>Enthusiastic and positive team player with a “No task is too small attitude”</li><li>Organized and detail oriented, able to prioritize and meet deadlines.</li><li>Willing to learn</li></ul>",
